title: Total vehicles entering Canada in Canada 2021
summary: The graph shows the Total Number of Canada vehicles in each of the months during 2021 .
The maximum Number of Canada in a Month has been recorded for August .
From February to August , this Number has been continuing to grow .
gold: The total vehicles entering Canada line chart demonstrates the number of entering in every month in 2021 . Overall , the number of entering rises continuously through the year , but there are some fluctuation back and forth occurs in Mar and Aug . In the end of Dec , the number of entering reached to 1.1e6 vehicles entering .
